Document: AudioEffectHighPassFilter  
Path: godot/classes/class_audioeffecthighpassfilter.rst  
Summary: A high-pass filter that attenuates low frequencies while allowing higher frequencies to pass unchanged, useful for creating space for bass and impact sounds.  

A "high-pass" filter attenuates frequencies lower than AudioEffectFilter.cutoff_hz and allows higher frequencies to pass unchanged. This filter can be used to remove "strength" from a sound, and give low-end space for basses and impact sounds. Note: The cutoff frequency is controlled via the AudioEffectFilter.cutoff_hz property.
